{
  "stem": "1860.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 411.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By-- at that time, one didn't need a ticket.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You just jumped from train to it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "First, we spent in Prague about three or four weeks running from one kitchen soup to another kitchen soup.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we managed to-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to travel to-- to Holland, to Rotterdam.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we contacted this gentlemen, my-- my father's business acquaintance.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he helped us a little bit, but not too much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Basically, we-- we contacted the organization for the refugees, and we were placed in a home for repatriates in-- in Rotterdam.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that's where we stayed for almost a year, nine months or so, waiting for the papers to come from the States.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My father and brother were already in-- in United States.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we as a first and second preference quota.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My-- my mother as a wife and I as a daughter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We received our visa and passports.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I want to go back some.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew-- Krakow was not a home anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- we have no place, really, to go back to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- we knew that our place is in the United States where my father is.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we knew that-- yes, that--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I am trying to think.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Probably, when we were in [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Wolbrum, ?] some kind of-- there was some kind of a correspondence that they-- they left for-- I'm trying to think whether they were in Africa or they were-- no, we had a-- we had news that I had an uncle living in-- in the United States.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or maybe even the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they knew-- maybe, even this gentleman in Rotterdam was the contact.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And through him, we knew exactly where my father is.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father-- this was a different story.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
